<section class="jumbo">
    <h1 class="slogan">Tindpet, matching people with their future life mates.</h1>
<p class="intro">Tindpet was born in 2023 for those people who want to find a new pet in their area. This website helps connect animal protectors with future adopters quickly and easily. The protector receives your request for interest in an animal and contacts you.
Unfortunately, new homeless animals appear every day, so our website is tremendously dynamic and full of new opportunities. </p>
</section>

<div class="pets">
  {{#each pets as |pet|}}
    <div class="pet" style="background-image:url('{{pet.image}}')">
      <div class="bgcolor">
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <p class="title_pet">{{pet.name}}, {{pet.age}}</p>
        <div class="detail">
          <a href="/pets/{{pet.id}}">Detail</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {{/each}}
</div>